snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Holi Re Rasiya
snippet.description:
After making India dance to its catchy beats in Season 1, ‘Holi Re Rasiya’ is back with Maithili Thakur, Seedhe Maut and Mahan Sehgal to throw the most colourful Holi party on the internet with Coke Studio Bharat. 

To make the celebrations grander, we are joined by internet sensations Sonal Devraj,  Saransh Goila, Saloni Gaur, Kashika Sisodia and Abhi Badarshahi.  

Originating from a bhajan, 'Holi Re Rasiya' is reimagined and recreated with lush soundscapes, where high energy beats meet the authenticity of classic folk instruments to create the perfect festive tune. A festival celebrated by people from all walks of life alike, get ready to move to the anthem of Holi parties this year!

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | MAGIC | Diljit Dosanjh x The Quickstyle
snippet.description:
Love stories from the heartland have inspired generations across the globe. Bringing real magic from the pind of Punjab to the world stage. The OG 'Lover' himself, Diljit Dosanjh is back at Coke Studio Bharat to show us how to fall in love all over again. Relive the moment of your first infatuation, of falling in love through the depth of your eyes. Uplifting this song with their electrifying presence ‘The Quick Style’, make you groove and an add a whole lot of heart to the first song of Coke Studio Bharat 2024

localized.title: Coke Studio Bharat | MAGIC | Diljit Dosanjh x The Quickstyle
localized.description:
Love stories from the heartland have inspired generations across the globe. Bringing real magic from the pind of Punjab to the world stage. The OG 'Lover' himself, Diljit Dosanjh is back at Coke Studio Bharat to show us how to fall in love all over again. Relive the moment of your first infatuation, of falling in love through the depth of your eyes. Uplifting this song with their electrifying presence ‘The Quick Style’, make you groove and an add a whole lot of heart to the first song of Coke Studio Bharat 2024
